flowchart TD
  Start([Start]) --> Initiate[Ordering Department initiates stock check]
  Initiate --> Find[System filters candidate sites trading items]
  Find --> Filter[Generate filtered item list per candidate site]
  Filter --> Send[Send stock inquiry requests to candidate sites]
  Send --> Query[Sites query local database for quantities]
  Query --> Reply[Sites reply with in-stock quantities]
  Reply --> Consolidate[System consolidates site responses]
  Consolidate --> Persist[System persists in Inventory Info File]
  Persist --> End([End])
